<i>adjective</i>: 활발하다 [활발하다], 활달하다 [활딸하다], 활기차다 [활기차다], 쾌활하다 [쾌활하다], 씩씩하다 [씩씨카다], 시퍼렇다 [시퍼러타], 성하다 [성ː하다], 말똥하다 [말똥하다] <i>adverb</i>: 펄떡펄떡 [펄떡펄떡], 팔딱팔딱 [팔딱팔딱], 팔딱 [팔딱] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>활발하다 [활발하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lively; cheerful; outgoing; vigorous</dd><br>
<dd>생기가 있고 힘차다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being full of life and energy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. active; busy</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이 많이 이루어지거나 벌어지다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being characterized by vigorous activity or frequent occurrence of a event.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>활달하다 [활딸하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. broad-minded; great-hearted</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 넓고 크다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being broad-minded and big-hearted.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vigorous; lively; outgoing</dd><br>
<dd>활발하고 명랑하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being lively and cheerful.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>활기차다 [활기차다]</dt><br>
<dd>energetic; lively; vibrant</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 넘치고 생기가 가득하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Full of power and vitality.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>쾌활하다 [쾌활하다]</dt><br>
<dd>cheerful; lively</dd><br>
<dd>명랑하고 활발하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Merry</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>씩씩하다 [씩씨카다]</dt><br>
<dd>lively; spirited; energetic</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 태도가 힘차고 활기차며 굳세다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's behavior or attitude being vigorous, powerful, and strong.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>시퍼렇다 [시퍼러타]</dt><br>
<dd>1. deep blue</dd><br>
<dd>빛깔이 매우 퍼렇다.</dd><br>
<dd>A color being extremely blue.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deadly pale</dd><br>
<dd>춥거나 겁에 질려 얼굴이나 입술 등이 매우 퍼렇다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's face, lips, etc., being deep blue because one is cold or scared.</dd><br>
<dd>3. sharp</dd><br>
<dd>칼날 등이 매우 날카롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>A blade, etc., being very keen.</dd><br>
<dd>4. furious; fiery</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 무서울 만큼 기세가 높고 표정이나 눈빛이 사납다.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) One's spirit being overwhelmingly high and one's look or eyes being fierce.</dd><br>
<dd>5. lively</dd><br>
<dd>멀쩡하게 살아 있거나 아주 생생하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Living without any problems or very fresh.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성하다 [성ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lively; flourishing</dd><br>
<dd>기운이나 세력이 한창 왕성하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Energy or force being strong.</dd><br>
<dd>2. thick; dense</dd><br>
<dd>나무나 풀이 싱싱하게 우거져 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Trees or grass having grown thick and green.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>말똥하다 [말똥하다]</dt><br>
<dd>lively; animated; alert; wide-awake</dd><br>
<dd>눈빛이나 정신 등이 생기가 있고 맑다.</dd><br>
<dd>Eyes or mind being vital and clear.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>펄떡펄떡 [펄떡펄떡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hoppingly; lively</dd><br>
<dd>자꾸 크고 탄력 있게 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing someone or something jumping heavily, bouncingly, and repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. angrily</dd><br>
<dd>매우 화가 나서 참지 못하고 자꾸 펄펄 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one's state of being very angry and repeatedly expressing one's anger, rather than controlling it.</dd><br>
<dd>3. with a throb</dd><br>
<dd>심장이나 맥박이 자꾸 크게 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one's heart or pulse throbbing heavily and repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>팔딱팔딱 [팔딱팔딱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hoppingly; lively</dd><br>
<dd>작고 탄력 있게 자꾸 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing someone or something jumping lightly, bouncingly, and repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with a throb</dd><br>
<dd>심장이나 맥이 작게 자꾸 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one's heart or pulse throbbing lightly and repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. angrily</dd><br>
<dd>화가 나서 참지 못하고 팔팔 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one's state of being angry and repeatedly expressing one's anger, rather than controlling it.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>팔딱 [팔딱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hoppingly; lively</dd><br>
<dd>작고 탄력 있게 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing someone or something jumping lightly and bouncingly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with a throb</dd><br>
<dd>심장이나 맥이 작게 뛰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one's heart or pulse throbbing lightly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>